    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👻 <strong>A unique cooperative horror RPG</strong><br>Whispers in the Dark is an online horror game where you manage a <strong>paranormal agency</strong>. With your teammates, explore haunted locations, gather clues, and face terrifying entities. Your progression relies on an <strong>innovative research system</strong> that expands your Codex, skills, and equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📚 <strong>A research system that changes everything</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Missions</strong> → unlock new maps and paranormal cases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skills</strong> → develop your abilities and unlock new tools.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Entities</strong> → study and identify the 12 ghosts, revealing their sensitivities and curses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚒️ <strong>Full RPG progression</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn experience and spend <strong>skill points</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your playstyle (investigator, tool specialist, hardened survivor).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip up to <strong>8 skills</strong> to create a unique role within the team.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔧 <strong>Evolving equipment</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a wide range of tools (EMF, candle, ghostly book, UV camera, etc.).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each item comes in <strong>three qualities</strong>: cheap (fragile), good (reliable), or <strong>excellent/legendary</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rare artifacts like the <strong>Montserrat Crucifix</strong> can turn the tide of a mission.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏚️ <strong>Co-op horror with replayability</strong><br>Each investigation is different: phenomena, behaviors, and clues vary with your choices and progression.<br>Survive, banish, or seal the entity within its <strong>hearth</strong> (fetish object)… if you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔑 <strong>Key features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online co-op for <strong>1–4 players</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative research system (missions, skills, entities, items)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG progression with XP, skill points, and specializations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over <strong>12 entities</strong> with unique spells, sensitivities, and behaviors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tools with <strong>3 quality levels</strong> (common → legendary)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic, oppressive atmosphere with high replay value</p></li></ul>",
